* phase-6 part-4: debug schema (enabled with -g).  Code-section labels become
* EXST statement entries (with their statement line in LINENUM); the absolute
* EQU symbol KON, a non-code symbol, becomes a VREBL variable entry.  One LOGBLK
* descriptor frames both (STSIZE = #EXST, VASIZE = #VREBL); the names go in the
* DBGNAM record and each EXST/VREBL entry points at its name.
       OUNAME DBGTEST
KON    EQU   5
START  LDA   DAT
       ADA   KON
LOOP   TRA   LOOP
DAT    OCT   7
       END   START
